RACE.FOOTNOTES: LUV MAP was off a step slow at the start, rushed up while racing five wide into the first turn, took over the lead near the midway point, lost command turning for home, stayed within striking distance, dug back in gamely and got up late. HOT SUMMER DREAM led the way in early stages then lost command to LUV MAP midway up the backstretch, remained up close then took back control entering the lane, led the way by a slim margin then got denied in final strides. SAENGER STAR settled through early stages, saved ground around the final turn, raced in contention and sustained a steady bid. BOOTLEGGING GIRL tracked the early pace, hustled up two wide late on the far turn then flattened in the lane. COWGIRLLOVER raced four wide around the first turn and raced in range up the backstretch, given cue late on the far turn and failed to respond. SOPHIE'S STAR raced in the back throughout.

ENTRY.OWNER: Murphy Travis Swan and Trent Matt
ENTRY.COMMENT: early lead, led stretch, denied late

ENTRY.COMMENT: settled early, inside 2nd turn, stayed on

ENTRY.OWNER: Murphy Travis Swan Trent Matt and Triple V Racing LLC
